The example below shows the correct format:

surface_reaction( &quot;CO(s) =&gt; CO + Rh(s)&quot;,
                   Arrhenius(1.00000E+13, 0, 133.4,
                             coverage = [&#39;CO(s)&#39;, 0.0, 0.0, -50.0]) )


